Cepta looked at the guns and then back at Dead-End, and realized that she 
couldn't answer his question. She didn't know what her alliegence was. In 
fact, she didn't know anything before waking up in this pod. Her programming 
had some holes in it, so she was missing quite alot of data.

"I .. I don't know." She replied, moving back a bit in the pod to get as far 
as she could from the guns.
